quoteText: Analytical data does not move outside Netsyms servers, and you cannot be identified with it.
title: The service does not use third-party analytics or tracking

tosdr.case: The service does not use third-party analytics or tracking platforms
tosdr.tldr: "Analytical data does not move outside Netsyms servers, and you cannot be identified with it.  If you don't want to be tracked at all, enable Do-Not-Track in your web browser or [click here](https://netsyms.com/tracking-opt-out/) to opt out."
